title: She's Going On A Romantic Getaway With The Man She Wants To Dump
description:
She wanted to break up with her boyfriend, but she procrastinated! Now, she’s all set to go on a romantic weekend getaway with him and another couple, and it’s about to be SUPER uncomfortable.
